{"tid":1641752,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"話說有冇手足幫到手？","createTime":"2019-10-09T12:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T16:55:14.000Z","uid":320827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57aa2ec06dfa2ce5bc5e0a0e0f85297f2a19a004","tid":1641752,"uid":320827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"學校就嚟陸運會，成間學校平衡時空咁。<br />\n我哋from又要啦啦隊比賽要叫一段長口號<br />\n我想用呢段長口號泥做下宣傳，放啲暗喻喺入面(太直接學校唔批<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n我想用藏頭詩之類嘅嘢<br />\n我諗左一句，之後乜都諗唔到，有冇手足可以幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n_ _班係_ _（學校名)之<span style=\"color: red;\">光</span><br />\n_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _<span style=\"color: red;\">復</span><br />\n<br />\n手冇手足可以幫手接落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e682401154a8010626a9fafd0fb7c875264385","tid":1641752,"uid":320827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"7f5173ae5faf2a3ef755fb60e98fe3640091267a","tid":1641752,"uid":320827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"871cbb7c0367f753da70b68ce0a307a3dc899bc5","tid":1641752,"uid":320827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"db43d427603662a28fa1cfa14a6e038f8edaaba2","tid":1641752,"uid":320827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"fcfae64fca206e335b729d787ee3e172c118e929","tid":1641752,"uid":320827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"a6998a91f1fae4e7b4384716c3809e8a8e933aa1","tid":1641752,"uid":320827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"acad8c7f2ae7b60d1d40f0b77e6a11d1c57da319","tid":1641752,"uid":320827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi